goToSleep() - Method in class main.CrewMember
Allows crew member go to sleep if actions are not maxed
Sleeping decreases tiredness by 12%
If tiredness is less than 0, set to default; 0%
Sleeping maximises actions and member will not be able to do anything unless it is the next day
